58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-03-29/ty-article/.highlight/ukrainians-are-like-kids-waiting-for-someone-to-save-us-israelis-are-more-like-adults/0000018e-870a-d641-abee-cfafa1130000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》10月7日调查了哈马斯性侵事件，然后麻烦就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-york-times-investigated-hamas-sexual-assault-on-oct-7-then-the-trouble-started/0000018e-86a2-d9dd-a39f-cee2043d0000</link><description>这家颇具影响力的报纸对哈马斯对以色列人的性侵犯的调查一开始就很复杂。很快，在亲巴勒斯坦活动人士的攻击下，记者们发现自己也成为了故事的焦点</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 22:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-york-times-investigated-hamas-sexual-assault-on-oct-7-then-the-trouble-started/0000018e-86a2-d9dd-a39f-cee2043d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>